    "description": "Crawling Silence is a survival horror game featuring an online co-op and singleplayer escape mode.. When playing, the players must find clues and solve puzzles to uncover the secrets hidden within the building. During your exploration, you must find one of multiple ways out of the building, utilizing items randomly hidden around the map. But beware, mistakes may alert creatures hiding behind every corner....<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The setting</h2>Crawling Silence is set in an old, long forgotten building shrouded in mystery, the secrets of which you must uncover.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873810/extras/51667b4f6073834cc02ff6edbfd167a2.poster.avif?t=1752596292\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873810/extras/51667b4f6073834cc02ff6edbfd167a2.webm?t=1752596292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873810/extras/51667b4f6073834cc02ff6edbfd167a2.mp4?t=1752596292\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >But beware, various dangerous creatures may lurk in the dark...</h2>The monsters you encounter while uncovering the secrets within the building have full access to vents, rooms and secret areas, so be cautious...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873810/extras/fc3fd140a382da0e30a947f0f32f3335.poster.avif?t=1752596292\" width=576 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873810/extras/fc3fd140a382da0e30a947f0f32f3335.webm?t=1752596292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873810/extras/fc3fd140a382da0e30a947f0f32f3335.mp4?t=1752596292\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873810/extras/320f1590dbc8e0a61ca0a357f3ddb03d.poster.avif?t=1752596292\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873810/extras/320f1590dbc8e0a61ca0a357f3ddb03d.webm?t=1752596292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873810/extras/320f1590dbc8e0a61ca0a357f3ddb03d.mp4?t=1752596292\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve riddles and find clues to advance in the story</h2>Many elements of the game are puzzle based<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873810/extras/70aaa5e477b93e97efc30d1bf9640679.poster.avif?t=1752596292\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873810/extras/70aaa5e477b93e97efc30d1bf9640679.webm?t=1752596292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873810/extras/70aaa5e477b93e97efc30d1bf9640679.mp4?t=1752596292\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find hidden passages</h2>There are various hidden doors and passages which you can discover, and maybe find helpful clues or items!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873810/extras/01b9ebd599dfdf52350326ee0d834d5e.poster.avif?t=1752596292\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873810/extras/01b9ebd599dfdf52350326ee0d834d5e.webm?t=1752596292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873810/extras/01b9ebd599dfdf52350326ee0d834d5e.mp4?t=1752596292\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Additionally, you will discovery things that may be used for your advantage...</h2>or they will turn against you, and force you to react quickly!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873810/extras/e773b65af97f594eb4e2c8fd481d8d4f.poster.avif?t=1752596292\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873810/extras/e773b65af97f594eb4e2c8fd481d8d4f.webm?t=1752596292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873810/extras/e773b65af97f594eb4e2c8fd481d8d4f.mp4?t=1752596292\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
